# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# AETHERIA ENVIRONMENT CONFIGURATION
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in the sacred keys
#
# For local development: .env.local
# For production (Netlify): Set these in Netlify Dashboard > Site Settings > Environment Variables

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# CONVEX - The cosmic backend
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Development: Get this from running `npx convex dev`
# Production: Get this from Convex Dashboard after creating a production deployment
PUBLIC_CONVEX_URL=https://your-project.convex.cloud

# Production deployment key (only needed for Netlify CI/CD)
# Get this from: Convex Dashboard > Settings > Deploy Key > Create Deploy Key
# Add to Netlify as: CONVEX_DEPLOY_KEY
# CONVEX_DEPLOY_KEY=prod:your-deploy-key-here

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# OPENROUTER - The gateway to AI vessels
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Get your key from: https://openrouter.ai/keys
# NOTE: This goes in CONVEX environment variables, not here!
# Add to Convex Dashboard > Settings > Environment Variables
# OPENROUTER_API_KEY=sk-or-v1-your-key-here
